event.logging

Class BaseChat

  • java.lang.Object
    • event.logging.BaseObject
      • event.logging.BaseChat
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    Chat, GroupChat

    public abstract class BaseChat
extends BaseObject
    Describes the details of a chat event, e.g. an instance message chat message from one user to another.

    Java class for BaseChat complex type.
